ftware development; cloud management; and application managed services, as well as AMC services, and hardware and software. Further, the company provides digital marketing services, search engine optimization, search engine marketing, social media marketing, e-commerce design and development, media buying, and web design and development. Olatech Solutions Limited was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Navi Mumbai, India."}}